    "actual_capabilities": [
      "Explains ShellCheck installation on macOS, Linux, and from source",
      "Provides .shellcheckrc configuration examples with enable and disable options",
      "Shows environment variable configuration for ShellCheck behavior",
      "Documents common error codes with code examples and fixes",
      "Offers CI/CD integration patterns for GitHub Actions and GitLab",
      "Describes output formats including GCC, JSON, and quiet modes"
